data.title: Memorial Weekend Bash Music Festival
meta_keywords: One of the biggest Tejano music extravaganzas in the country is back for 2024! Come on down to beautiful Riverside Park in Victoria
TX for three days of music
data.meta_description: One of the biggest Tejano music extravaganzas in the country is back for 2024! Come on down to beautiful Riverside Park in Victoria, TX for three days of music, great food, and family fun.
data.text:
Location(s):

Riverside Park - 361-485-3200

Don't miss one of the largest Tejano music extravaganzas in the entire state! Featuring live performances by some of the biggest names in the Tejano scene, including Siggno, La Mafia, Jay Perez, Duelo and many more. Get VIP tickets for the ultimate experience!

The event also features a BBQ cookoff, car show, inflatable kids' activities, cool vendors, and so much more!

Hotel specials are available for this event. Enjoy all three days of fun in Victoria! See full list below:
